sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as Training Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Master as PyTorch Master Pod<br/>23456/TCP
    participant Worker1 as PyTorch Worker Pod 1<br/>23456/TCP
    participant Worker2 as PyTorch Worker Pod 2<br/>23456/TCP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>HTTP Scrape

    %% Flow 1: Training Job Creation
    rect rgb(200, 220, 240)
        Note over User,Operator: Flow 1: Training Job Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: POST PyTorchJob CR<br/>Auth: User Token
        K8sAPI-->>User: 201 Created
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event<br/>PyTorchJob Created
        Operator->>K8sAPI: GET PyTorchJob Spec<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: PyTorchJob Details
        Operator->>K8sAPI: POST Pods (Master + Workers)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS1.2+
        Operator->>K8sAPI: POST Services (Headless)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS1.2+
        Operator->>K8sAPI: POST ConfigMaps<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS1.2+
        Operator->>K8sAPI: PATCH PyTorchJob Status<br/>Status: Running
    end

    %% Flow 2: Distributed Training
    rect rgb(220, 240, 200)
        Note over Master,Worker2: Flow 2: Distributed Training Communication
        Master->>Worker1: Initialize Training<br/>23456/TCP (plaintext)
        Master->>Worker2: Initialize Training<br/>23456/TCP (plaintext)
        Worker1->>Master: Gradient Sync<br/>23456/TCP
        Worker2->>Master: Gradient Sync<br/>23456/TCP
        Worker1->>Worker2: All-Reduce Communication<br/>23456/TCP
        Worker2->>Worker1: All-Reduce Response<br/>23456/TCP
    end

    %% Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    rect rgb(240, 220, 200)
        Note over Prometheus,Operator: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (plaintext)
        Operator-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics<br/>job_count, reconciliation_duration
    end

    %% Flow 4: Job Completion
    rect rgb(240, 200, 220)
        Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Job Completion
        Master->>Master: Training Complete
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch Pod Events<br/>Pod Succeeded
        Operator->>K8sAPI: PATCH PyTorchJob Status<br/>Status: Succeeded
        Operator->>K8sAPI: DELETE Pods (optional cleanup)
    end
